title_ssm: Tradition of Excellence: The Sesquicentennial History of the University at Albany, State University of New York, 1844 to 1994
scopecontent_ssm: Contains all chapters of the published book as well as most of the photographs that it featured.
bioghist_ssm: The university commissioned a history to celebrate its 150th anniversary in 1994. A Tradition of Excellence was researched and written by history professor Kendall Birr and edited by Vincent Reda.
